## Ready ##
## Triggers when the DOM is ready to be manipulated (IE is 100% effective) ##
$(document).ready ->

  ## Products ##
  ## This has to be bound to the body tag for now ##
  products = $("body").attr("data-products-count") || 0

  ## Button Disable ##
  ## Required if we don't have any products ##
  if (products <= 0)
    $("#sync_all").attr("disabled", true)
    $("#delete_all").attr("disabled", true)

  ## Mutation Observer ##
  ## We need to track the "toolbar" to make sure that "destroy_all" doesn't appear if the system has no products

